Weapon Stats                                
=====================================================================
This help is to be used as a guide for making weapons.  The point of 
this is to keep the mud in balance.  The following shows the damdice
to use for it's level.  DO NOT use any other values.  Round to the 
nearest level if the weapon is inbetween.


